{"tid":1107111,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"死神擦身過！山路盲彎逆線爬頭　兩車險迎頭對撼","createTime":"2019-04-15T04:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T13:26:48.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a17817670ee16474795ee111e05624fa23cff7","tid":1107111,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"死神擦身過！山路盲彎逆線爬頭 兩車險迎頭對撼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Gbw530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Gbw530&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUakPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f6925500\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Gbw530</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190415/photo/bkn-20190415114006941-0415_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190415121226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190415%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190415114006941-0415_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190415121226&h=a9ca76d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再開快啲隨時出事！<br />\n<br />\n上周六（13日）下午約2時半，當時正下着毛毛細雨，有私家車司機載着家人，沿大潭道往赤柱方向行駛。惟當他駛至一彎位時，驚見前方有私家車疑為爬頭，越過雙白線逆線行駛，兩車險些迎頭對撼。幸他反應及時，立即煞車。"},{"pid":"940f1dfe4a98f6fc9a317e83d718869c9b03a37b","tid":1107111,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"每逢星期日都總有啲司機為咗威畀女仔睇/為咗出位而做出以上嘅危險動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe7968be9f46f0bf1e14b8b9b08f36d97531194","tid":1107111,"uid":162910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"打咩格仔<br />\n真係要投訴佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449e922799b2d253c8edce1c73718b767ca3c23f","tid":1107111,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"MK GOLF"},{"pid":"89b3a2708b30543e767b70c9ee438df67f57acf4","tid":1107111,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"轉彎位逆線爬頭啲人根本唔適合揸車"},{"pid":"5fbd7